 over the English until he was eventually defeated by  King Harold  in  1063 ."]},{"name":"Griffith","meanings":["Anglicized form of   Gruffudd ."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"When Catrin verch Gruffudd was born in 1210, in Wales, her father, Gruffudd Gwyr ap Cydifor, was 40 and her mother, Catrin verch Elidir Marchog, was 41. She married Rhys ap Hywel in 1255, in Wales. They were the parents of at least 3 sons. She died in 1261, in Brecon, Breconshire, Wales, at the age of 51."},"et":{"1210–1261":"1210–1261","1198–Male":"1198–Surnud","1200–Male":"1200–Surnud","1207–Male":"1207–Surnud","1210–1255":"1210–1255","1294–1328":"1294–1328","–Male":"Surnud","1230–Male":"1230–Surnud","1234–1279":"1234–1279","1170–Male":"1170–Surnud","1170–Female":"1170–Surnud","22 May 1255":"22. mai 1255","1198":"1198","1230":"1230","1261":"1261","1294":"1294","1170":"1170","ABT 1230":"umbes 1230","1279":"1279","1234":"1234","1255":"1255","1200":"1200","1210":"1210","1328":"1328","1207":"1207","Brecon, Breconshire, Wales":"Brecon, Breconshire, Wales","Wales":"Wales, United Kingdom","Aberllynfi, Breconshire, Wales":"Aberllynfi, Breconshire, Wales, United Kingdom","Llanspyddid, Breconshire, Wales":"Llanspyddid, Breconshire, Wales","Glasbury, Breconshire, Wales":"Glasbury, Breconshire, Wales"},"fi":{"1210–1261":"1210–1261","1198–Male":"1198–Kuollut","1200–Male":"1200–Kuollut","1207–Male":"1207–Kuollut","1210–1255":"1210–1255","1294–1328":"1294–1328","–Male":"Kuollut","1230–Male":"1230–Kuollut","1234–1279":"1234–1279","1170–Male":"1170–Kuollut","1170–Female":"1170–Kuollut","22 May 1255":"22. toukokuuta 1255","1198":"1198","1230":"1230","1261":"1261","1294":"1294","1170":"1170","ABT 1230":"noin 1230","1279":"1279","1234":"1234","1255":"1255","1200":"1200","1210":"1210","1328":"1328","1207":"1207","Brecon, Breconshire, Wales":"Brecon, Breconshire, Wales","Wales":"Wales, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Aberllynfi, Breconshire, Wales":"Aberllynfi, Breconshire, Wales, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Llanspyddid, Brecon